1972 - 2012
Much loved and missed
by family and friends near and far

See the blue moon stripe the water.
Hear excited children's laughter,
Build your memories for ever after.
Climb the trees, the red rocks too,
Do all the things I loved to do,
I share these happy days with you"∫
